        <h2 id="do-i-need-government-gateway">Do I need Government Gateway to use GOV.UK?</h2>
        <p>No, you don't need a Government Gateway account to use GOV.UK. </p>
        <p>Some of the tools and services we link to from GOV.UK may use a Government Gateway account for you to log in, but we will make sure this is noted on GOV.UK before you visit that site.</p>

        <h2 id="who-can-fix-government-gateway">Who can help fix the problems I'm having logging in to Government Gateway?</h2>
        <p>You can contact the Government Gateway team via the 'helpdesk' link on the Government Gateway website: <a href="http://www.gateway.gov.uk/">http://www.gateway.gov.uk/</a>.</p>

      </div>
    </article>

  </div>
</section>

